title: x-mirage (Registered)
description:
Here's x-mirage, one of the best software you will find to emulate airplay on your mac.
"X-Mirage is the most professional AirPlay server for Mac and Windows PC, which allows you to wirelessly stream contents or mirror iPhone, iPad and iPod screen to any Mac/Windows PC. Record screen and audio from iOS devices, as well as voiceover via Microphone with one click." - x-mirage.com
